snippet.title: Soviet (Opera Soft) (1990) (Amstrad CPC)
snippet.description:
(See all text for Spanish)
Aunque me quedo con la colorida versión de Spectrum, en Amstrad CPC, Soviet impresionante técnicamente hablando, aunque muy difícil.

Although I prefer the colourful Spectrum version. In Amstrad CPC, Soviet is technically impressive, but very difficult.
